they could
actually be forced to stomach
some pretty

07:30.216 --> 07:32.619 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
substantial cuts in the coming
years.

07:32.652 --> 07:38.591 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
