48:24.969 --> 48:32.209 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then I -- in the middle of
that phrase,
I sort of went -- and I
harmonically went

48:32.243 --> 48:46.824 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
