48:55.633 --> 48:58.836 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Is that an
intellectual process
that he just described, where he
switches

48:58.869 --> 49:01.071 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
