happens?

49:01.105 --> 49:02.873 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JOSHUA REDMAN: That's an
excellent question.

49:02.907 --> 49:07.244 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
