it's an intellectual
process, then I'm not
successful.

49:07.278 --> 49:08.546 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: It's not going to
work.

49:08.579 --> 49:11.148 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JOSHUA REDMAN: It's an
emotional, it's an
intuitive process.

49:11.182 --> 49:16.787 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
