49:23.794 --> 49:30.835 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BRAD MEHLDAU: It's very exciting
to really
improvise, and to have that
moment.

49:30.868 --> 49:32.736 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And it's also very social music.

49:32.770 --> 49:34.572 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
