very -- it's

49:42.246 --> 49:43.414 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
pretty exciting.

49:43.447 --> 49:45.282 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOSHUA REDMAN: It's a great time
