50:45.442 --> 50:50.447 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Joan Cartan-Hansen of Idaho
Public Television
has been following the man
tasked with finding

50:50.481 --> 50:52.816 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
