profile.

50:52.850 --> 50:57.221 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOAN CARTAN-HANSEN: Chris
Niccoli's day job
is fighting wildfires out of the
smokejumpers

50:57.254 --> 50:58.756 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
