a new assignment.

51:01.692 --> 51:07.998 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRIS NICCOLI, U.S. Forest
Service: I'm also
the logistic section for the
U.S. Capitol

51:08.032 --> 51:09.667 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Christmas Tree.

51:09.700 --> 51:12.469 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
