better, yes.

52:16.100 --> 52:17.167 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CHRIS NICCOLI: Yes.

52:17.201 --> 52:18.268 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
