52:18.302 --> 52:21.438 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TED BECHTOL: A nice looking
tree.

52:21.472 --> 52:23.307 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
CHRIS NICCOLI: It's a good
looking tree.

52:23.340 --> 52:26.310 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOAN CARTAN-HANSEN: Just as
important as finding
the right tree is finding it in
the right

52:26.343 --> 52:28.078 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
